description: Built in 2020, this home boasts upscale finishes across its almost 1,400SF. From the gorgeous white oak floors to the inviting open concept living and dining area, every detail in this home exudes elegance. The kitchen is a chefs haven featuring Thermador appliances & quartz countertops that seamlessly connect to the open living space. Custom built-ins enhance the fireplace, adding a touch of sophistication. Journey down the hallway to the first bedroom, where two custom closets and ample natural light create an inviting ambiance. Ready to unwind? Head up to the primary suite oasis on the upper level with room for a king-sized bed & an ensuite bathroom boasting a double vanity and a steam shower. Discover an additional bonus space, perfect for an office or custom designed extra closet. Enjoy two private outdoor spaces, garage parking and extra storage.  Nestled in an ideal location near the Broadway T stop, Seaport & Fort Point areas, and major routes like 93 & 90.
